{"tid":2366492,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完月色真美, 好有共嗚","createTime":"2021-01-14T14:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T14:38:47.000Z","uid":130565,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"13b1b8fed8b5a3638a8931c1c6ddaa533eced845","tid":2366492,"uid":130565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T14:01:43.000Z","msg":"睇完幾日心入面仲未安靜落黎, 想呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讀書曾經主動追個女仔, 我同佢都怕羞唔太講野. <br />\n最開始我地係由Whatsapp傾計. 佢係group度問野, 我私底下WhatsApp教佢. 我同佢之間就係咁開始. 之後開始見面都會傾下一兩句計. 但佢唔太講野, 身邊得一個女仔friend.  我地都係係手機入面好傾得, 但現實就算見到都講唔到幾句. 身邊朋友都知我中意佢, 佢生日我都送禮物俾佢.<br />\n最後因為畢業, 佢打算做野, 我打算繼續讀書. 我覺得就算一齊左都維繫唔到, 就順其自然咁分別, 到最後都無表白. 而佢係一排後Whatsapp問我最近點, 呢段就係我地最後既對話.<br />\n如果我好似男主咁早啲表白, 最後既結果會更好.<br />\n<br />\nBTW 依家同緊另一個, 但Long D 緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7c76e3be4df2c280f25097f37e8088117e9000","tid":2366492,"uid":135986,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T14:04:04.000Z","msg":"睇完套野你冇諗到現家long D個個<br />\n<br />\n咁你要認真考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ab216b96b75f2edfafc67d2eaed820fd3a92c5","tid":2366492,"uid":12421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a7c76e3be4df2c280f25097f37e8088117e9000","tid":2366492,"uid":135986,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T14:04:04.000Z","msg":"睇完套野你冇諗到現家long D個個<br />\n<br />\n咁你要認真考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T14:08:26.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明套嘢個結局係long D但結到婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befe008a1266d78c3c283e6f66463c742a55d27d","tid":2366492,"uid":316697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88ab216b96b75f2edfafc67d2eaed820fd3a92c5","tid":2366492,"uid":12421,"